Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.56,0:00:17.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少女作為超世脫俗的天才兒童
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.44,0:00:19.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被寄養在設施中
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.58,0:00:21.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}時間是在一歲之前
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.66,0:00:26.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少女開始會說話之後不久
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:33.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}她在那裡得知了遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.39,0:00:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}稱之為智能檢查
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.51,0:00:39.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}她被人要求玩了許多遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.90,0:00:40.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是太過無聊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.31,0:00:42.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不論跟誰玩都感覺不到快樂
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.71,0:00:47.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}之後 在過了兩年之後
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.20,0:00:51.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少女和似乎是母親的女性再會了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.23,0:00:55.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}比自己年長七歲的少年
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.32,0:00:59.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在大人們的對話中 適當地附和著
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.26,0:01:02.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}展露出空虛且無感情的笑容 面對這樣的他
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.40,0:01:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}少女張開了長時間閉住的嘴
Dialogue: 0,0:01:09.28,0:01:11.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是個空殼
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.07,0:01:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吶 我們來玩遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.51,0:01:45.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.11,0:01:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(640,670)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:47.11,0:01:48.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}『　　』
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(615,670)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:50.54,0:01:51.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對『　　』來說…
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\blur2\pos(615,670)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.13,0:01:53.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對『　　』來說…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:08.90,0:02:10.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是做了惡夢吧
Dialogue: 0,0:02:11.58,0:02:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我就去端暖和的牛奶
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.57,0:02:14.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:14.61,0:02:15.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.06,0:02:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}他是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.22,0:02:18.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們一直在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:02:18.52,0:02:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.05,0:02:19.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.60,0:02:25.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.11,0:02:29.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白！
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.17,0:02:39.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好涼
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.32,0:02:44.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主人 您在這裡嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:44.81,0:02:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小多拉驚惶失措地說您突然飛奔出來
Dialogue: 0,0:02:47.96,0:02:48.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我在想您是怎麼了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.33,0:02:50.04,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吉普莉爾
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.63,0:02:52.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在的 您有什麼事？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.94,0:02:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吉普莉爾的主人是誰？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.30,0:02:58.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼現在要特地問這種事…
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.30,0:02:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回答我
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.53,0:03:02.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是白大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.06,0:03:06.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼和吉普莉爾戰鬥的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:06.86,0:03:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是白大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.30,0:03:12.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要求史蒂芙迷上我的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.38,0:03:14.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}聽說是白大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.61,0:03:17.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}揭露了東部聯合的遊戲內容的是？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.75,0:03:20.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是白大人與小多拉祖父的遺物
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.46,0:03:24.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我吉普莉爾
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.06,0:03:28.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}欽佩白大人那舉世無雙的才智和智謀
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.07,0:03:30.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以跟隨了您
Dialogue: 0,0:03:31.33,0:03:32.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}跟隨了白？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.70,0:03:34.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(670,670)}<Immunity>
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.55,0:03:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}作為艾爾奇亞的王 人類種的全權代理人——
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.94,0:03:39.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白大人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:43.32,0:03:46.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是說 除了白以外還存在其他人
Dialogue: 0,0:03:47.14,0:03:48.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是沒有根據
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.32,0:03:50.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}城內當然不用說
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.69,0:03:59.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an8\fs36}門牌：白的家
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.74,0:03:54.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}儘管將詢問範圍擴大到城鎮周邊的所有地方
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.65,0:03:55.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.82,0:03:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在抗議遊行之中也沒有人知道那個人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.49,0:04:01.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這麼說
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.94,0:04:03.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}恐怕是
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.34,0:04:08.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主人在我們不知道的一段時間內和什麼人進行了遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.78,0:04:11.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}失敗後被人篡改了記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.96,0:04:14.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼會 這種事到底是…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.17,0:04:17.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}東部聯合
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.58,0:04:17.87,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.30,0:04:19.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果是他們的話 應該是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.65,0:04:25.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主人
Dialogue: 0,0:04:26.89,0:04:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們來遊戲吧
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.33,0:04:34.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.71,0:04:34.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是的
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.56,0:04:39.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}賭上灌輸給主人的虛偽的存在進行遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.08,0:04:40.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虛偽？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.35,0:04:43.18,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然後 雖然十分失禮
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.36,0:04:45.91,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能請您輸給我嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.75,0:04:50.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼 遊戲就決定是國際象棋了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.49,0:04:53.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}虛偽的存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.00,0:04:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那真的是 虛偽的？
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.56,0:05:00.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.70,0:05:01.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}才會漸漸消失？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.63,0:05:09.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吶 白
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.38,0:05:13.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雖然有人說人是會改變的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.28,0:05:15.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但真的是這樣嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.14,0:05:19.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全部 全部…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.00,0:05:20.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}都在漸漸消失
Dialogue: 0,0:05:22.28,0:05:24.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果許願說想要飛翔
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.26,0:05:25.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就能長出翅膀嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.93,0:05:27.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我認為是不會的
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.68,0:05:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}應該改變的不是自己
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.45,0:05:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}而是手段吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.79,0:05:33.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.36,0:05:35.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}只有去創造
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.32,0:05:40.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}創造出現在的自己能夠飛上天的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:05:41.91,0:05:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}讓白飛上天的翅膀
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.86,0:05:46.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur3}慢慢地思考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.88,0:05:51.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}全部都是虛偽…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.16,0:05:55.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一切都是謊言…
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.52,0:05:59.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}消失了的話就會輕鬆…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:05.97,0:06:06.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(630,670)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:08.01,0:06:09.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}『　　』？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.51,0:06:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主人？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(640,670)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.09,0:06:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}『　　』
