Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.36,0:06:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對『　　』來說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fs32\blur2\pos(615,670)}空白
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.27,0:06:21.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對『　　』來說…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.73,0:06:25.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒有失敗
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.93,0:06:43.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼要取勝呢
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.30,0:06:46.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥——空是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.71,0:06:50.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}絕對 絕對是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.47,0:06:50.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}空？
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.37,0:06:53.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主人 但是…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:52.70,0:06:54.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\move(640,666,640,710,520,920)\blur2}存在 是存在的！
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.53,0:06:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請冷靜下來 主人
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.54,0:06:57.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}請合乎邏輯地考慮…
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.38,0:06:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}的確
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.63,0:07:03.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}的確認為不存在才是理所當然的
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.31,0:07:06.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但那個人一定存在
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.62,0:07:08.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小多拉 妳在說什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.97,0:07:12.51,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因為 不可能輸的嘛
Comment: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}••
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.03,0:07:13.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白他們
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.23,0:07:16.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}史蒂芙…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.70,0:07:17.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.77,0:07:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒錯 不可能輸
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.48,0:07:21.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}一定有什麼緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.76,0:07:23.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}創造出這個狀況的緣故
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.92,0:07:26.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}妳太任憑感情行事了 再多…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.64,0:07:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}妳們兩個人
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.15,0:07:29.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}昨天在做什麼？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.57,0:07:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}昨天？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.57,0:07:33.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}忙於處理遊行活動
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.93,0:07:35.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那之後和白在王座上玩遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.13,0:07:38.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是前天 十九日
Dialogue: 0,0:07:40.04,0:07:41.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}改變提問
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.71,0:07:43.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}前天的晚上妳在哪裡
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.06,0:07:47.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是那天晚上的事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.45,0:07:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那個 那個 誒？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.88,0:07:51.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}記憶…
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.44,0:07:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒有了 這就好
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.17,0:07:54.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.96,0:07:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}之後只剩下確認
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.76,0:08:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那個 妳在做什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:04.05,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我在摸史蒂芙的胸部
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.36,0:08:07.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼 我該怎麼反應…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.62,0:08:09.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}妳不興奮嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.77,0:08:12.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明明我對妳說過迷上我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.83,0:08:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.69,0:08:18.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是「除了主人之外 有要求小多拉迷上他的人」
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.44,0:08:21.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒錯　因為這麼要求的是哥
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.08,0:08:25.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 空的存在不是已經確信了嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.32,0:08:29.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我到底是為了什麼而被揉了呢
Dialogue: 0,0:08:30.24,0:08:34.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是謝禮 因為要是沒有史蒂芙我就察覺不到了
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.56,0:08:36.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白…
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.61,0:08:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼試著想想看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.66,0:08:43.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}存在空這個人並且消失的可能性
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.60,0:08:49.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}大約一天半 從我們所有人腦中消失的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.73,0:08:53.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雖然使用大規模的魔法並不是不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.87,0:08:56.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但那樣的話一定會留下痕跡
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.63,0:08:59.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是遊戲的話？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.03,0:09:01.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.86,0:09:08.01,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要是有向盟約宣誓後進行的遊戲中有這樣的設定呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.69,0:09:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果是作為全權代理人進行的遊戲的話
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(785,670)}<Immunity>
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.56,0:09:15.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}其影響會波及所有人類種
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.96,0:09:17.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是對吉普莉爾…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.92,0:09:20.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 在侍奉主人的現在
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.84,0:09:22.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我換而言之就是附屬物
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.24,0:09:25.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}應該可以考慮成受到其影響
Dialogue: 0,0:09:26.25,0:09:27.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}原來如此
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.28,0:09:30.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 這到底是什麼遊戲呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:31.67,0:09:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我不知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:34.88,0:09:36.30,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:09:36.80,0:09:37.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.92,0:09:41.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我相信著白
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.13,0:09:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白 我們兩人無論何時都是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.20,0:09:49.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥不會讓白一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.83,0:09:51.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.45,0:09:54.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白… 妳在嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.78,0:09:57.97,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白 妳還在嗎…
Dialogue: 0,0:09:59.42,0:09:59.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.73,0:10:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白 妳在哪裡 妳能握緊我還有知覺的地方嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.91,0:10:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為了讓我不瘋掉
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.39,0:10:14.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥
Dialogue: 0,0:10:19.19,0:10:19.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白…
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.28,0:10:24.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就算燒壞也可以 思考吧
Dialogue: 0,0:10:25.36,0:10:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這個狀況——哥所託付給我的這個狀況
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.30,0:10:31.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}使用一切剩下的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.66,0:10:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥是存在的
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.51,0:10:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們兩人是一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.09,0:10:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這樣的話 哥就在這裡
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.73,0:10:43.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥說過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:44.11,0:10:46.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}總是在遊戲開始之前就獲勝
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.39,0:10:49.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因約定而結合在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.88,0:10:54.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥說過
Dialogue: 0,0:10:55.62,0:10:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我們不是少年漫畫的主人公
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.62,0:11:01.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不行 再多思考
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.99,0:11:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}再多多思考
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.45,0:11:04.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥說過
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:06.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}去拿下最後一塊拼圖
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.96,0:11:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}拿下？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.72,0:11:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為此進行的遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.76,0:11:14.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}與東部聯合的戰鬥所需的手牌
Dialogue: 0,0:11:15.40,0:11:18.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}道具 智慧 監視者
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(620,670)}<Elf>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.20,0:11:19.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}森精種？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(715,670)}<Elf>
Dialogue: 0,0:11:21.46,0:11:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為了得到森精種
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.23,0:11:23.88,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要怎麼得到
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.64,0:11:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}向愛爾文•加爾得挑戰
Dialogue: 0,0:11:27.89,0:11:28.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.06,0:11:29.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是的
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.95,0:11:31.66,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}克拉米並不相信哥
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.26,0:11:34.00,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不可能會答應這種要求
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.52,0:11:44.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相互爭奪存在的遊戲 的話
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.98,0:11:49.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白
Dialogue: 0,0:11:50.11,0:11:50.86,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白！
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.74,0:11:56.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}相互爭奪存在的遊戲？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.84,0:11:57.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.09,0:12:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs28\pos(1030,538)\fad(800,300)}<Sky•Walk>{\fs40}\N分離法
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.50,0:11:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.20,0:12:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}構成自己存在的三十二個棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.70,0:12:05.67,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}反映出心理深層次的優先順序
Dialogue: 0,0:12:06.27,0:12:08.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}按照重要的順序 從一開始分配
Dialogue: 0,0:12:09.21,0:12:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是說 哪個棋子構成著自己的什麼部分
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.85,0:12:16.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在被對方取得之後 確確實實失去後才會知道
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(705,670)}<Elf>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.45,0:12:20.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}比如說 妳旁邊森精種的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.14,0:12:23.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}手臂和腳 神經和記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.77,0:12:29.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然後就連存在本身都會被剝奪 完全認知不出
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.78,0:12:31.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是說 會消失
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.18,0:12:33.22,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你是認真的嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.72,0:12:34.13,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.80,0:12:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}盟約其五 被挑戰的一方擁有遊戲內容的決定權
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.46,0:12:41.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不願意的話 遊戲不會成立
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.74,0:12:43.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}妳要怎麼做？
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.10,0:12:44.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(780,670)}<Immunity>
Dialogue: 0,0:12:45.84,0:12:50.29,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}菲 這個男人在宣言賭上人類種的棋子
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.76,0:12:52.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不能放著他不管
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.80,0:12:55.41,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是的
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.98,0:12:59.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}明明我還有些期待著是不是能夠和解
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.49,0:13:00.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我接受和解
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(765,670)}<Elf>
Dialogue: 0,0:13:01.40,0:13:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果妳能相信我把那個森精種讓給我
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.06,0:13:06.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我怎麼可能這麼做
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.07,0:13:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我猜也是
Dialogue: 0,0:13:08.70,0:13:09.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你賭上的東西是？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:09.89,0:13:13.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}贏的一方能要求對方兩件事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.08,0:13:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}比如說 將遊戲結果永久確立
Dialogue: 0,0:13:17.54,0:13:20.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}將對方的存在永遠葬送
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.78,0:13:23.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}篡改彼此夥伴的一個記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.73,0:13:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}使她成為同伴
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.66,0:13:31.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}也就是說 爭奪雙方的存在和同伴生死的權利嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:31.71,0:13:32.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒錯
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.41,0:13:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你簡直是瘋了
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:42.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那麼 因為瘋了順便提案一條重要的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.72,0:13:45.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.82,0:13:47.38,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主人
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.38,0:13:48.03,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:49.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}妳沒事吧
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.34,0:13:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.71,0:13:54.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吉普莉爾
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.97,0:13:56.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}您有什麼事
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.93,0:13:59.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能做出相互爭奪存在的遊戲嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.70,0:14:02.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不 很遺憾
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:06.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果是實體化首尾接龍那樣的虛擬世界的話 是可能的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(589,670)}<Elf>
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.57,0:14:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果和森精種一起合作呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:08.28,0:14:09.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}合作？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.07,0:14:12.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}和那些森林裡的鄉下人嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.16,0:14:13.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}在遠古大戰的時候
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.54,0:14:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被我的一發天擊連國都被轟飛的像垃圾一樣的存在…
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.21,0:14:17.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}能做到嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.59,0:14:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是不可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.42,0:14:27.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那群鄉下人對編織複雜的術式多少還是很擅長的
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.94,0:14:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那空就是進行了那個遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.77,0:14:32.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然後消除了自己的存在
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.64,0:14:33.19,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.68,0:14:34.59,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}既然如此的話
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.73,0:14:39.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那果然是已經輸了然後存在被消除了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.47,0:14:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是啊
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.69,0:14:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果勝利了的話空應該是存在的才對
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.07,0:14:47.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}如果既不是贏了也不是輸了的話呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.99,0:14:48.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哈？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.57,0:14:51.54,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}遊戲還在進行中
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.57,0:14:52.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.33,0:14:54.17,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼可能
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.45,0:14:57.83,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}吉普莉爾 魔法的反應 這間房間裡的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:00.18,0:15:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我明白了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.60,0:15:11.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白是在這裡醒來的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.68,0:15:14.61,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥和白的寢室 明明在別的地方
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.65,0:15:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是卻在這個房間裡
Dialogue: 0,0:15:17.56,0:15:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥說過不會讓我一個人的
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.61,0:15:26.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}確實有魔法在展開
Dialogue: 0,0:15:26.40,0:15:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不過精確的位置就…
Dialogue: 0,0:15:28.82,0:15:31.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}事到如此只有把所及之處都找遍了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.74,0:15:37.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}小多拉 竟然在什麼都沒有的地方摔倒
Dialogue: 0,0:15:38.12,0:15:40.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我認為已經不需要再增加角色設定了
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.12,0:15:43.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}摔倒了？ 我？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.08,0:15:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}黑白棋的棋子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(570,670)}<Elf>
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.13,0:15:50.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是森精種文字的三呢
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.14,0:15:52.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼只有棋子？
Dialogue: 0,0:15:54.64,0:15:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}因為還沒有被使用
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.77,0:16:00.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就算無法被認知但還是在那裡
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.44,0:16:06.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是 就算是知道了也只有三枚棋子而已
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.90,0:16:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}連我們這邊是執白還是執黑都不清楚
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那種事很簡單
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.37,0:16:16.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥說過 我們兩個人合起來才算一個人
Dialogue: 0,0:16:16.62,0:16:19.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這個遊戲白也參加在其中
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.46,0:16:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我提案一個非常重要的規則
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.00,0:16:25.37,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}雙方的夥伴也參加遊戲
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.42,0:16:29.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}當玩家無法繼續的情況下可以代打
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.86,0:16:34.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}所以記憶保留了下來
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.05,0:16:37.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看得到嗎？ 棋盤？
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.47,0:16:44.02,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看不見 但我知道哥的話會怎麼走
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.77,0:16:49.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}你這是故意輸給我的下法啊
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.78,0:16:53.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不是 這樣就是能贏的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.82,0:16:56.65,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎樣誘導對方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.33,0:17:03.08,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是什麼？你的記憶？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:03.33,0:17:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}難道你想讓我就這樣搶奪你的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.46,0:17:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然後證明背後沒有任何種族的事實嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.39,0:17:13.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不算壞的答案
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.80,0:17:16.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎樣傳達自己的目的
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.23,0:17:31.56,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這樣就無法繼續遊戲了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.77,0:17:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是我贏了
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.03,0:17:36.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}但是遊戲還沒有…
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.99,0:17:41.12,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎麼回事？ 為什麼遊戲還不結束？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.29,0:17:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那三枚棋子到底是空的什麼
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.79,0:17:50.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}怎樣欺騙對方
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.79,0:17:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然後 怎樣取得勝利
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.35,0:18:02.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥 很厲害哦
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.68,0:18:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這樣的話沒人能明白
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.15,0:18:09.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}除了哥和白以外
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.82,0:18:15.94,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}剩下的棋子裡所含有的構成哥的要素
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.16,0:18:16.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}那是——
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.74,0:18:22.49,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}第三 取得遊戲勝利的方法
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.53,0:18:29.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}第二 對白的絕對信賴
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.96,0:18:37.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然後第一 白個人的一切
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.26,0:18:41.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了 哥
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.85,0:18:45.47,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}回來吧！
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.09,0:19:15.84,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:21.85,0:19:22.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.22,0:19:26.14,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了 妳可以揍我
Dialogue: 0,0:19:26.31,0:19:27.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我已經做好覺悟了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.80,0:19:28.64,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.31,0:19:30.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.85,0:19:32.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.61,0:19:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}對不起
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.22,0:19:38.85,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白 應該更早一點 更早一點
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.82,0:19:43.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}竟然忘記了主人
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.78,0:19:45.20,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}為什麼呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.45,0:19:47.70,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}克拉米 振作一些
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.70,0:19:48.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.33,0:19:51.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:19:51.42,0:19:52.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.41,0:19:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好了 我要按照預定提出要求了
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.13,0:20:03.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我可以任你擺佈 但是克拉米…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.71,0:20:06.42,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不行 要求一
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.43,0:20:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不要啊
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.31,0:20:12.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}將雙方所爭奪的記憶 固定與歸還
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.93,0:20:16.48,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.53,0:20:18.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這到底是怎麼一回事
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.19,0:20:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}保留從對方那裡得到的記憶
Dialogue: 0,0:20:21.79,0:20:24.45,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}同時把被奪取的記憶還給了本人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.70,0:20:26.33,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這樣一來
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.45,0:20:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}克拉米和主人就成為了知曉對方一切的
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.91,0:20:32.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}值得信賴的同伴了
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.25,0:20:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這正是主人所追求的最後一片拼圖
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.50,0:20:38.25,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}然後…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs32\pos(700,670)}<Elf>
Dialogue: 0,0:20:38.88,0:20:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}要求二 那邊的森精種——菲爾
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.84,0:20:45.58,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我要獲得篡改你記憶的權利
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.59,0:20:46.23,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}什…
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.64,0:20:47.39,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒問題
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.06,0:20:49.31,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}沒關係的 菲
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.56,0:20:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這個男人的要求只有一個
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.57,0:20:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}就是要我們當間諜吧
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.69,0:20:59.44,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}不愧是偷窺過我腦中記憶的人
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.44,0:21:00.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}間諜？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.41,0:21:01.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這是怎麼回事？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.49,0:21:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}過後告訴妳
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.58,0:21:11.16,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}看過你腦中的記憶後 我改變了想法
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.74,0:21:12.79,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}我贊同你的計畫
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.84,0:21:16.50,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}哥 很厲害
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.09,0:21:18.34,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.46,0:21:21.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}妳可以誇我是可以引以為傲的哥哥哦
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.39,0:21:26.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}是白引以為傲的哥
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.93,0:21:31.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}被妳這麼老實地稱讚 哥會害羞的
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.89,0:21:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}主人
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.19,0:21:38.69,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}白 差不多可以了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:21:39.44,0:21:40.24,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}嗯
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.49,0:21:44.57,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}準備好了 隨時可以
Dialogue: 0,0:21:45.53,0:21:46.07,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}菲
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.20,0:21:47.99,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}克拉米
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.21,0:21:55.92,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}真是超可怕啊 真再也不會做這種事情了
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.42,0:21:59.26,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.42,0:22:03.68,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}到底是什麼啊
Dialogue: 0,0:22:05.14,0:22:07.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}這也是主人真正的姿態…
Dialogue: 0,0:22:08.43,0:22:09.75,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}…也說不定呢
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.80,0:22:17.40,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好可怕啊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.44,0:23:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\an7\fs36}註：出自聖龍戰記
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.44,0:23:50.27,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}比Salamander還要快得多
Dialogue: 0,0:23:50.28,0:23:51.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}好囉嗦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:49.89,0:23:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\pos(617,348)}請稍後
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.20,0:23:52.95,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2}成為大人真是悲傷
Dialogue: 0,0:23:47.88,0:23:52.89,Default,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fs28\pos(1064,541)}<Blue・Rose>{\fs40}\N指向法
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.23,0:22:45.70,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}誰にも言えない孤独を抱えたまま一人で泣いてた
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.70,0:22:57.66,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}誰にも上手に笑えない僕ら二人出会って笑った
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:23:04.00,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}真夜中すぎに　想像の奥に
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:09.03,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}どうしようもない気持ちをただ押しやって
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:14.90,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}サヨナラ　僕らはきっと生まれ変われるから
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.90,0:23:18.98,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}悲しみに手を振るんでしょう
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.98,0:23:25.79,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}そしていつか空っぽのままの心に灯りをともすように
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:32.18,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}とぎれとぎれの　言葉を探して繋ぎ止めた
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.18,0:23:38.05,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}それでもたった二人の世界は続いてくんだ
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.05,0:23:46.76,EDJP,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}空に祈るように　どうか永遠に
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.23,0:22:45.70,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}將無法對別人說出口的孤獨藏於心中 一個人哭泣
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.70,0:22:57.66,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}無法對別人好好笑出來的我們 相遇了歡笑了
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.20,0:23:04.00,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}在午夜過後之時 在想像深處之中
Dialogue: 0,0:23:04.00,0:23:09.03,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}只是將無可奈何的心情拋在一邊
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.03,0:23:14.90,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}再見了 因為我們一定能夠重獲新生
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.90,0:23:18.98,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}對悲傷揮揮手吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.98,0:23:25.79,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}然後曾經空蕩蕩的心靈就會像點燃了明燈一樣
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.49,0:23:32.18,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}尋找斷斷續續的話語 將它們系在一起
Dialogue: 0,0:23:32.18,0:23:38.05,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}儘管如此兩人的世界還是會繼續
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.05,0:23:46.76,EDCH,,0,0,0,,{\blur2\fad(150,150)}像天空祈禱 請一定要相伴永遠
